# Cursor Rules - Insight Contract Intelligence Platform

## TAILWIND COMPONENT DESIGN PATTERN

### Never Use Raw Tailwind in Pages
```tsx
// ❌ BAD
<div className="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 p-4">

// ✅ GOOD
<Grid columns={3} gap="lg" padding="md">
```

### Layout Components
- Use `Grid`, `GridItem` from `@/components` for grid layouts
- Use `Stack`, `HStack`, `VStack` for flex layouts
- Use Catalyst components: `Card`, `CardHeader`, `CardBody`, `PageHeading`

### Size Tokens
Use semantic sizes, not raw Tailwind:
- `none`, `xs`, `sm`, `md`, `lg`, `xl`, `2xl`

### Color Tokens
Never use raw colors in pages/domain components:
| BANNED | USE INSTEAD |
|--------|-------------|
| `text-emerald-*` | `text-success` |
| `text-rose-*` | `text-danger` |
| `text-amber-*` | `text-warning` |
| `text-cyan-*` | `text-accent` |

## STRICT TYPESCRIPT

### No Any
Never use `any`. Use `unknown` with type guards.

### Strict Boolean Checks
```tsx
// ❌ BAD
if (data) { }
if (!isLoading) { }

// ✅ GOOD
if (data !== undefined && data !== null) { }
if (isLoading === false) { }
```

### No Unchecked Indexing
```tsx
// ❌ BAD
items[0].id

// ✅ GOOD
items.at(0)?.id
```

## COMPONENT ARCHITECTURE

### Catalyst First
Use Catalyst UI Kit components from `src/components/catalyst/`

### No Naked HTML
Raw HTML only allowed in:
- `src/components/catalyst/`
- `src/components/layout/`
- `src/components/ui/`

Pages and domain components must use layout/Catalyst components.

## FILE ORGANIZATION

- Types in separate `.types.ts` files
- Exports only through barrel `index.ts`
- Cognitive complexity limit: 15
